result.name: 兄弟得記燒臘飯店

reviews.text:
Such excellent food! You'd never expect it, but you can get a real authentic taste of Hong Kong cuisine at this small yet mighty neighbourhood shop. The barbecued meats are fresh, juicy, and perfectly grilled. It's so tasty that you'll learn to savour every bite. 

As an additional bonus, there's also a lively and spirited atmosphere that goes extra well with the local delicacy. Easily recommended, and five stars all the way!
reasonably priced with supreme quality,great place for authentic cantonese food👍🏻👍🏻a must try👍🏻

One of my favourite local restaurants that served traditional barbecued food. It was next to Times Square shopping mall and was conveniently adjacent to the Causeway Bay MTR station.

Food was very decent, serving in generous portions and the staffs were as friendly as in family. Their signature combo comprised different delicious small bites with steam rice, and was of great value.

Visitors should try to avoid two things: 1) visit there during official lunch hours (12nn - 2pm) on weekdays - since it located at the heart of the commercial area, the crowd would be quite intimidating.

2) sharing of table should be expected; similar to most local restaurants, visitors may not experience 100% top notch hygienic environment (food was perfectly fine), or a romantic ambiance for a date.

This restaurant was a shop with caring heart and support for the democratic movement of Hong Kong 🇭🇰.
One of the best value for money Cantonese Siu Mei eatery in the city.
Must try local barbecue meat. Very authentic cantonese food. been there a few times. Cha Siu really good!

reviews.text:
Such excellent food! You'd never expect it, but you can get a real authentic taste of Hong Kong cuisine at this small yet mighty neighbourhood shop. The barbecued meats are fresh, juicy, and perfectly grilled. It's so tasty that you'll learn to savour every bite. 

As an additional bonus, there's also a lively and spirited atmosphere that goes extra well with the local delicacy. Easily recommended, and five stars all the way!

叉燒好食， 肥瘦適中， 仲食到蜜汁味
白切雞都啖啖肉，味道還可以
價錢方面， 係銅鑼灣黎講算抵了
Anyway,  最難得係一班明白事理既師傅，五星！

食咗十幾年嘅得記，雖然呢幾年唔响銅鑼灣返工，佢哋堅有人情味。燒味當然好味，我最鐘意嘅燒肉切肶飯加凍檸茶外賣，我响舖頭打電話叫送上office，叔叔仲要同我鬥快上到去，好懷念！
聽埋條片，又勾起我嘅回憶。

比連銷式飲食集團更值得大家支持，
用料新鮮，火候控制得不錯，味道很好份量又多，奶茶有茶香口感細滑，令人回味。銅鑼灣想吃燒臘/醫肚，記得支持下本地良心食店。
👨🏻‍🍳👨🏻‍🍳👨🏻‍🍳有種味道比珍饈更可貴更能滲透人心。
成日黎食早餐 當然燒味都好好 有人情味
